                                                                               "details":  {
                                                                                               "body":  "\u003cp\u003eThe minister is responsible for international defence engagement, defence export campaigns outside the Gulf, Defence Infrastructure Organisation, including delivery of the basing strategy, and Scotland.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003ePriority areas:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eDefence Engagement Strategy\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003edefence infrastructure and delivery of the basing strategy\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eScotland\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOther responsibilities include:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003edefence export campaigns outside the Gulf\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eNATO transformation and reform\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eEU relations\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ecounter-proliferation, arms control and disarmament\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003einformation management\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStrategic Defence and Security Review (SDSR) preparation\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003easset disposal, including PEX(A) lead\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAlso: Prime Minister’s Special Representative for centenary commemoration of World War 1.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n",
